WEBVTT

00:00:00.433 --> 00:00:04.237
Upon request, the Employee and the Local Union can have access

00:00:04.304 --> 00:00:09.142
to the position description; an evaluation report, if available,

00:00:09.209 --> 00:00:11.511
organizational and functional charts;

00:00:11.578 --> 00:00:15.782
and information directly related to the classification for the position.

00:00:15.849 --> 00:00:18.585
They can work with facility Department Officials to perform

00:00:18.651 --> 00:00:20.854
an informal classification review.


